History
=======

0.1.0 (2023-09-27)
------------------

* First release on PyPI.

0.2.0 (2023-09-27)
------------------

* Hydrobot now annals the "Processor" class, which has capabilities to process data within the single object. Class_script gives an example of this method of processing.

